name: Rune Dragon - The first BRC333 Audio PFP collection
description: Egg333 is a 10k collection of BRC333 dynamic collectible eggs that hatch before the halvening. The longer it cooks, the rarer the collectible. The top 30% rarity get a Rune symbol. After the hatching inscription, there will be a reinscription that brings your creature to life in a more advanced state.
